time of filing this report. The incident was however, confirmed by a senior police officer in the Ughelli Area command. UGHELLI, headquarter of Ughelli North Local Government Area, Delta State, was, yesterday, thrown into mourning, following the murder of Mr. Emmanuel Akaranwuan, a vhief nursing officer attached to the Mariere Central Hospital, Ughelli. December 2, 2010 In "News" ONE person was last Tuesday killed by unidentified gunmen in the Ojokor area of Ughelli, Delta State in what sources described as a cult related attack. May 30, 2018 In "Crime Alert" UGHELLI—The family of slain Vice Chairman of Oteri community in Ughelli North Local Government Area of Delta State, Blessing Unuesefe, has petitioned the Inspector General of Police, Mr. Abba Suleiman over his killing by security agents. February 27, 2015 In "News"